---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Nicolai Valenta" description="Sophomore Philosophy major at UT Austin in the Liberal Arts Honors Program, with minors in Economics and Entrepreneurship.">
  <main class="about-page">
    <header class="about-header">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-content">
      <section class="bio">
        <p class="lead">
          Sophomore Philosophy major in the Liberal Arts Honors Program at the University of Texas
          at Austin, pursuing minors in Economics and Entrepreneurship.
        </p>
        <p>
          Drawn to philosophy as a rigorous foundation for thinking about ethics, consciousness,
          and the long-term trajectory of human society &mdash; particularly as AI and technological
          change strain existing institutions. I study economics to understand how value flows through
          markets and governments, and where misaligned incentives produce dysfunction.
        </p>
        <p>
          I believe the most pressing problems facing society sit at the intersection of policy and
          entrepreneurial thinking, and that durable reform requires both philosophical clarity about
          what's worth building and the practical knowledge of how institutions actually work.
        </p>
      </section>

